PrecisApproval (a) to enter into an AGREEMENT with LA COOPÉRATIVE BAIE BLEUE LTÉE which provides for the implementation of a cooperative plan for the marketing of WILD BLUEBERRIES produced in NEW BRUNSWICK during 1992, and (b) to appoint SERVICES UNIS DE VÉRIFICATION ET D'INSPECTION, chartered accountants, to inspect and audit the books and accounts of the aforementioned cooperative association.
